Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.74,0:00:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? A massive Roman Army\Ncontingent has appeared
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.04,0:00:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,at the Seize border with No Man's Land?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.22,0:00:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aisha!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.13,0:00:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that gunshot?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.59,0:00:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've secured a Roman soldier!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.71,0:00:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.71,0:00:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, still breathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.48,0:00:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well done!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.28,0:00:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will now rendezvous with the\N1st and 3rd divisions on the border-
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.94,0:00:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing-
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.89,0:00:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.12,0:00:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move and I'll shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.24,0:00:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.60,0:01:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Colonel, please escort your\Nmen outside the fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.19,0:01:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fill the Blue Sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.78,0:01:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Betrayal!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.75,0:01:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The girls took our commander hostage\Nand barricaded themselves in the fort!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.72,0:01:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.56,0:01:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fortunately, it missed her internal organs.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.80,0:01:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, for the moment, she should be OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.96,0:01:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Yumina-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.68,0:01:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.32,0:01:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll be a sacrifice to start the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.34,0:01:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She'd be worth less to us dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.79,0:01:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.39,0:01:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the last month, we've followed the\Napproaching Roman army from the rear.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.18,0:01:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably nothing more than a display of power\Nto give them an advantage in the peace talks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.59,0:01:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They must think we're fools.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.57,0:02:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the Archduke insisted we do nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.87,0:02:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we needed something to\Npush them to attack us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.48,0:02:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like a sobbing POW executed\Nright in front of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.25,0:02:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't intend to-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.52,0:02:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The peace talks are a farce!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.48,0:02:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rome must be destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.26,0:02:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right, Noël Kannagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.38,0:02:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, my dear ally, the witch of Helvetia.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.11,0:02:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You thought I wouldn't notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.69,0:02:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.71,0:02:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just used her!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.96,0:02:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noël-san, you have something to do\Nwith the Invisible Reaper?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.67,0:02:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Invisible Reaper?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.47,0:02:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl there was one of the greatest\Ngeniuses in academy history,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.15,0:02:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the one who revived the Invisible Reaper,\Nan old-era bioweapons plant.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.78,0:02:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your talent is still valuable.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.17,0:02:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.14,0:03:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha-chan, toss him in the\Nunderground distillery.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.82,0:03:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My comrades are already deploying\Nto fight the Romans.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.79,0:03:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One small spark is all that's needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.76,0:03:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back to the battlefield, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.97,0:03:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was finally over...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.66,0:03:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've both got crap for luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.45,0:03:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've locked the Colonel inside the distillery.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.90,0:03:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Kureha-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.22,0:03:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have something to eat...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.70,0:03:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some cookies I got at Treize!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.92,0:03:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.99,0:03:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naomi-san, you're still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.96,0:03:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave if it gets dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.45,0:03:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is really messed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.35,0:04:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Flame Maidens are supposed\Nto protect the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.78,0:04:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're getting them involved in battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.83,0:04:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.48,0:04:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was hiding, I asked Aisha-san about\Nthe legend of the Flame Maidens.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.68,0:04:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And she said that the Romans tell\Na totally different legend...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.23,0:04:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.29,0:04:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Flame Maidens protect others' lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.30,0:04:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.41,0:04:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time to switch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.62,0:04:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.16,0:04:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't trust you out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.27,0:04:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For starters, can you even\Nfire a gun at anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.48,0:05:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I think it's the right thing\Nto do, I might be able to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.69,0:05:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.09,0:05:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a fortress maiden, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.19,0:05:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like our forerunners, the Flame Maidens...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.81,0:05:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.94,0:05:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You believe that arbitrary\NRoman fairy tale?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.35,0:05:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.75,0:05:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels right to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.20,0:05:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Flame Maidens protect others' lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.84,0:05:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that just might be the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.43,0:05:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.21,0:05:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.92,0:05:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hear what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.99,0:05:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.52,0:06:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care how good her ears are,\Nshe can't hear you from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.75,0:06:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A signal to stop fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.38,0:06:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! I heard it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.80,0:06:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.92,0:06:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.01,0:06:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too early to be happy about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.54,0:06:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She might have imagined it,\Nand even if not,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.53,0:06:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we don't know it means the\Npeace talks are over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.74,0:06:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, we need to tell Colonel Hopkins-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.73,0:06:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.00,0:06:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I went to take food to the\NColonel, and he was gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.88,0:06:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you're safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.64,0:06:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We strike in ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.99,0:06:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Colonel!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.22,0:06:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think they'll listen?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.20,0:06:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's worth a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.78,0:06:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.97,0:06:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.35,0:06:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Colonel was laughing...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.46,0:07:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When he saw my Reaper\Nkill all those people,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.27,0:07:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he was laughing so hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.45,0:07:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll kill... He'll fight until no one is left.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.99,0:07:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I helped him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.27,0:07:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.89,0:07:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you think that, then save more\Nlives than you've taken, Noël-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.99,0:07:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aisha...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.47,0:07:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cease-fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.12,0:07:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.60,0:07:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But her ears are that good!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.83,0:07:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.57,0:07:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll vouch for her!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.00,0:07:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a tiny kid, and she forgets stuff,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.00,0:07:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and isn't sexy at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.97,0:07:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She wouldn't lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.04,0:07:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arrest everyone here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.62,0:07:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want war that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.61,0:07:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,War advances civilization and science.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.83,0:08:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to bring back the glory\Nhumanity once had.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.25,0:08:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.45,0:08:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Romans are going to attack\Ntomorrow morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.73,0:08:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, there's no way to stop the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.24,0:08:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naomi-san was arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.25,0:08:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.28,0:08:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.42,0:08:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Demon of Vingt!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.98,0:08:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I want to deliver the\Nsound I've been given!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.63,0:08:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just selfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.78,0:08:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's selfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.29,0:08:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you make that decision yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.79,0:08:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're soldiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.57,0:08:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone was saying the world is ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.22,0:08:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I like this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.84,0:08:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.59,0:08:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love the people here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.47,0:09:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.99,0:09:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.35,0:09:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.95,0:09:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.04,0:09:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aisha-san was saying the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.60,0:09:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.10,0:09:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a soldier, I have killed people, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.36,0:09:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.63,0:09:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...just like...you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.72,0:09:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have suffered enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.83,0:09:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have suffered enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.40,0:09:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So even if no one else forgives you, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.65,0:10:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So even if...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.58,0:10:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You forgive me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.16,0:10:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Aisha.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.96,0:10:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we do this, there'll be no turning back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.57,0:10:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're OK with that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.02,0:10:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.09,0:10:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I've got nothing else to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.53,0:10:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.59,0:10:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Kureha-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.40,0:11:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For our sakes, you've always said\Nwhat you thought was best, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.89,0:11:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.14,0:11:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want a girl my age\Nto be tortured, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.94,0:11:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Rio-sempai's gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.24,0:11:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Noël and Kanata are such slackers...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.49,0:11:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I thought I had to do my best...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.43,0:11:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I'm such a bad captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.76,0:11:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.64,0:11:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.04,0:11:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May all of the Gods grant their\Nblessings to the Flame Maidens.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.38,0:11:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Primary converter reactor output rising.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.81,0:12:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,FAP, FAC, DMR, ECP all normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.73,0:12:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Superconductor circuit functioning\Nwithin stable parameters.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.28,0:12:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire control system's looking good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.02,0:12:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Primary and secondary cannons are online!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.32,0:12:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Release all joint locks!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.21,0:12:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Weight reduction system online.\NCoefficient is around five.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.46,0:12:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.92,0:12:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we just do it like in training, we'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.30,0:12:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, my girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.57,0:12:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.61,0:12:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare to fire main cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.53,0:12:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Load AP round!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.78,0:12:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,AP round loaded!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.95,0:12:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Target locked!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.38,0:12:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kana-chan, the signal!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.70,0:12:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.71,0:13:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Begin the attack"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.69,0:13:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.67,0:13:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Kanata-neechan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.02,0:13:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Takemikazuchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.67,0:14:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've restored so much of that\Nancient high technology.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.48,0:14:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Contact all tanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.32,0:14:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do everything you can to stop them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.99,0:14:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Begin the attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.46,0:14:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't let you through!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.74,0:14:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't want any more war!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.53,0:14:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.24,0:14:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll have to take us out first!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.83,0:14:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.53,0:14:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, what will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.33,0:14:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Demon of Vingt.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.44,0:14:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Circle around!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.52,0:14:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll meet up with the forces to our rear!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.83,0:14:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Flame Maidens protect others' lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.30,0:14:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rest is in your hands, Kanata-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.49,0:14:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Many years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.02,0:15:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,before the world became as it is now,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.64,0:15:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God sent an angel to punish the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.86,0:15:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The angel was wounded, and set his wings\Ndown to rest, at a western-end town.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.58,0:15:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was the maidens, who lived in the\Ncity's fortress, that saved him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.41,0:15:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was sent to destroy them,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.62,0:15:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but they took pity on his wounds
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.96,0:15:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gaining the help of a giant spider,\Nthey gave the angel refuge at the bottom of the valley.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.70,0:15:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Each, in turn, embraced the angel's neck,\Nto keep the blood from pouring out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.11,0:15:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In return, he gave them a golden horn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.72,0:16:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But eventually, the townspeople found\Nhim there. They set fire to the valley.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.66,0:16:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Burning the maidens, and\Ntaking the angel's head.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.87,0:16:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The legend says that then armies\Nof angels appeared, covering the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.66,0:16:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then a miracle occurred.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.50,0:16:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A glorious sound filled the air,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.14,0:16:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the angels left.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.76,0:16:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The last maiden had used her last breath\Nto sound the golden horn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.14,0:17:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you remember that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.71,0:17:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one you gave the caramel to?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.32,0:17:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll be caught up in this, too, won't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.46,0:17:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All troops, prepare to charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.45,0:17:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing to do about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.10,0:17:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.08,0:17:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.87,0:17:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.03,0:17:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.39,0:17:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an allied tank!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.85,0:17:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's with...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.04,0:17:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The 1121 Platoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.80,0:18:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the cease-fire signal!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.55,0:18:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.65,0:18:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Roman military signal!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.70,0:18:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.87,0:18:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't stop here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.01,0:18:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready the main cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.51,0:18:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... They won't stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.65,0:18:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.20,0:18:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kana-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.73,0:20:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.64,0:20:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.99,0:20:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.33,0:20:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.89,0:20:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both sides, lay down your weapons!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.31,0:20:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am second heir to the royal line of Helvetia
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.65,0:20:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and fiancée to the Holy Roman Emperor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.27,0:20:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio Kazumiya Arkadia!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.43,0:20:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I command you by the names of my father,\Nthe Archduke of Helvetia, and of the Roman Emperor!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.37,0:20:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The peace talks have ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.31,0:20:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is to be no more fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.91,0:21:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both sides are to disband immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.80,0:21:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a royal order!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.98,0:21:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who disobey will be punished by
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.35,0:21:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the first Helvetia Royal Guard,\Nin both leaders' names!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.58,0:21:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.98,0:21:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.98,0:21:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.19,0:21:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.10,0:21:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.25,0:21:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sergeant!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.23,0:22:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spring sure has sprung.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.43,0:22:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Noël,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.99,0:22:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that letter Aisha sent you...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.52,0:22:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did it say?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.34,0:22:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My wounds are healed, and I'm practicing\Nthe trumpet every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.50,0:22:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Translate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.22,0:22:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's doing well and practicing her trumpet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.09,0:22:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah? Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.22,0:22:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, we get letters from Rome\Nbut not from the capitol.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.54,0:22:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she's busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.73,0:23:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a princess now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.23,0:23:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But even on the battlefield,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.73,0:23:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she was surrounded by guards,\Nand we couldn't talk to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.08,0:23:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Claus's bike!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.40,0:23:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's here! She's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.02,0:23:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tell you how much I've been\Nlooking forward to the new girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.48,0:23:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to be really hard-
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.21,0:23:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Lt. Rio Kazumiya Arkadia. I have been transferred\Nto the 1121 Platoon as of today.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.13,0:23:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Filicia Heidemann, please\Ngive me permission to arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.00,0:23:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.43,0:23:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't use ranks here, Rio.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.40,0:24:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.12,0:24:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Roman Emperor is actually a decent guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.02,0:24:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he'd grant any wish I had,\Nas a reward for stopping the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.40,0:24:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.76,0:24:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.05,0:24:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.19,0:24:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.38,0:24:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, Rio.
